scene.message:
Nanjo: I was waiting.{waitkey}I came on ahead to give{nl}
you this.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's a "Phurba Dagger,"{waitkey}but it's awkward for me to{nl}
use, so I'll give it to you.{waitkey}{clearbox}No need for thanks. In return,{nl}
save the school as fast as{nl}
you can.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It seems touching this{nl}
transports you to another{nl}
place.{waitkey}{clearbox}Where it sends you, though,{nl}
I couldn't say.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Stare at it long{nl}
enough and it feels like it'd{nl}
suck you in.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Stare at it long{nl}
enough and it feels like it'd{nl}
suck you in.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: You're slow, honestly.{waitkey}{clearbox}I've got to keep watch over{nl}
Toro, so sorry, but I can't{nl}
come with you.{waitkey}{clearbox}To make up for it — you'll{nl}
need all sorts of things, so{nl}
here, take this!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's the "Scorching Tablet."{waitkey}I won it at the casino, and{nl}
I've got another one.{waitkey}{clearbox}Nah, no thanks needed. Now{nl}
go on, give it your all!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I've got to keep watch{nl}
