Elly: So you were here after{nl}
all. I came to give you this.{waitkey}It's the "Full Moon Tablet."{waitkey}{clearbox}I was looking for something{nl}
in the library and happened{nl}
upon it.{waitkey}{clearbox}I thought it would be of more{nl}
use in your hands.{waitkey}{ret}
